{"tid":797273,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"只要一停低就會諗起佢","createTime":"2018-08-28T11:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T15:24:58.000Z","uid":14549,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7ccfaa5cea13b3d68b1fbca7c21000399407629f","tid":797273,"uid":14549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T11:37:22.000Z","msg":"真係好懷念以前既日子<br />\n同佢睇戲 攬住佢 覺得好實在<br />\n好再想攬住佢訓<br />\n好想以後都一齊<br />\n好想同佢拖住手行街<br />\n點解由細到大都唔比父母重視<br />\n對呀哥有期望<br />\n對細佬寵愛<br />\n我係中間咩都得唔到<br />\n以為有女朋友之後可以感受到重視<br />\n可以將我擺第一位<br />\n結果都係一樣<br />\n點解個天對我咁唔公平<br />\n生到我一無是處 <br />\n當初我都唔想咁接近你<br />\n係你不斷去接近我<br />\n差唔多九個月我先肯忘記以前<br />\n想同你重新開始<br />\n但慢慢我覺得你係我全部既時候<br />\n你要咁恨心將我成個世界抽空<br />\n得返自己一個<br />\n每日自己一個 做咩都自己一個 永遠自己一個<br />\n每日期待既就係你既短信<br />\n其他人同我講咩都冇心機理<br />\n只係諗住你<br />\n真係好心痛<br />\n當初講到幾鐘意我 幾咁愛我<br />\n瞬間就可以話自己唔肯定係咪鐘意我<br />\n定你已經變左心<br />\n我真係好愛你架<br />\n到底點先可以忘記你"},{"pid":"c156d6e8dba8bc437b59b8336c2305f9ea12dc3c","tid":797273,"uid":140798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:26:08.000Z","msg":"變左心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb904db48550766a9447653a42592e07fffc786","tid":797273,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T13:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/28/212301_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F28%2F212301_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=933afcfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/28/212302_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F28%2F212302_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=70734b58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b26f533422e1cc1abf9ad49ae0cd821eadfdd04e","tid":797273,"uid":134445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T03:21:24.000Z","msg":"同樓主一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不停同自己講唔好諗 佢已經好決意分手<br />\n但自己都會每分每秒都諗住佢<br />\n佢就開開心心去玩 我就日日喊苦喊忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c74643eecca911946ba17317709d80134911fbd","tid":797273,"uid":77132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T15:24:58.000Z","msg":"你同我真係好撚似一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}